# 💰 AWS Budget Alarm Project

This project demonstrates how to set up a **monthly budget alarm** in AWS to monitor cloud spending and avoid unexpected charges—perfect for beginners using the AWS Free Tier.

## 📌 Project Goals

- Learn how to navigate the AWS Billing Dashboard
- Set up a cost budget with email alerts
- Practice using AWS Budgets and SNS (Simple Notification Service)

## 🛠️ Tools & Services Used

- **AWS Budgets**
- **AWS SNS (Simple Notification Service)**
- **IAM (for permissions)**
- **GitHub (for documentation)**

## 🪜 Steps Followed

1. Logged into the AWS Console
2. Navigated to **Billing > Budgets**
3. Created a **monthly cost budget** with a \$5 limit
4. Set up **email alerts** for 80% and 100% thresholds
5. Verified email subscription via SNS
6. Tested the alert by simulating usage (optional)

